Like, if you had to research ten different topics about a person and you were the only person in your group it would take a long time.  Most of the time, you have a limited time period to finish a assigment.  But if you have ten people doing the assigment it would take a shorter time because each person can research one topic at the same time.  Also, the quality if the work will be higher and better.  Sometimes when there is one person doing the work in a limited time he/she rushes.  And when you rush the quality of the work will not be as high and good as when you do it with a group.  And when you are in a company and the quality isn't good not a lot of people will buy the item or whatever the assigment or task was.
